snippet.title: Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet - Ambush of the Imposters DLC Trailer | PS4, XB1, PC
snippet.description:
With rumors of enemy ArFa-sys circulating throughout GGO, it is up to you and some renowned players to uncover the truth!  Jump into Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet's 1st DLC Chapter: Ambush of the Imposters today as the mystery unfolds and new challenges appear! 

Sword Art Online: Fatal Bullet Ambush of the Imposters DLC is AVAILABLE NOW! https://bandainam.co/SAOFB #FatalBullet
